setAuction.t.sol
├─ when the caller does not have the DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE
│  └─ it should revert
├─ when the caller does have the DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE
│  └─ it should revert
├─ when the auction contract is set to the zero address
│  └─ it should revert
└─ when the auction contract is not set to the zero address
   ├─ when the auction contract does not support the IBaseAuction interface
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ when the auction contract supports the IBaseAuction interface
      ├─ when the new auction contract is the same address as the one that is already configured
      │  └─ it should revert
      └─ when the new auction contract is different than the one already configured
         ├─ it should set the new auction contract
         └─ it should emit a AuctionContractSet event
